('COMBE DE JOB SARL', '21 Avenue Conseiller Coudert', '19130', 'OBJAT', '法国', '555841333', 'http://www.lacombedejob.com', 'La Combe de Job is located in Corrèze, in the south-west of France. Since 1979, we have used a specific method to produce their high quality products: the "artisan conserveur".We propose duck and goose specialities such as foie gras, patés and rillettes, ready-made meals, gizzards, sauces..\r\nWe also propose gourmet gifts. All their preserves are handmade as we remain faithful to the terroir and to authenticity.\r\nLa Combe de Job is also committed to innovation as they also produce mixed salades, duck paupiettes stuffed with foie gras.\r\nProduct range :\r\n- Foie gras (whole duck and goose foie gras, b-- LOCK duck foie gras...)\r\n- Specialities with foie gras (liver terrine with 50% foie gras, duck breast stuffed with foie gras, stuffed quail with foie gras...) \r\n- Patés and rillettes : limousin terrine with chesnuts and foie gras or with prunes and foie gras, duck terrine with black/green olives and foie gras, Correzien paté with smoked duck breast, duck rillettes with 20% foie gras\r\n- Ready-made meals : cassoulet with duck confit, goose confit, duck confit, preserved pork fillet...\r\n- Gizzards, sauces...\r\n- Gourmet gifts, business gift sets.', 'GOBERT', 'FABRICE', 'contact@lacombedejob.com', 'contact@lacombedejob.com', '', '', '巧克力、甜食、果酱、蜂蜜 - 即食菜肴（新鲜、冷冻或罐头菜肴） - 熟肉腌肉制品和罐头 - 精致香料产品', '欧洲', '比利时 -意大利 -荷兰', '2013-10-23 16:30:00', '2013-10-23 16:30:00'),
